{"TopicId":111158,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Ask the Mods questions about the Forums!","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-28T17:01:51Z","PageNum":178,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-06T10:28:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Apologies if this is the wrong place for this question, but is your username a reference to the character from the book The City and the Stars by Arthur C. Clarke?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: Oh hey, I made a new page.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-04-06T10:29:10Z\u0022 title=\u002204/06/2019 10:29  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EApril 6, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by RealKerbal3x\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-06T19:34:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223577204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554546526\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Apologies if this is the wrong place for this question, but is your username a reference to the character from the book The City and the Stars by Arthur C. Clarke?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: Oh hey, I made a new page.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes it is. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"roboslacker","CreatedById":175473,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-06T20:26:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you change the size of an image when posting it on the forum?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chemp","CreatedById":154483,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-06T20:45:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223577443\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554582364\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175473\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022roboslacker\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 minutes ago, roboslacker said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you change the size of an image when posting it on the forum?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDouble-click on it in the editor. You can change the size in the editor that pops up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022726\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/EroiXz8.jpg\u0022 style=\u0022width:375px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u0022750\u0022 alt=\u0022EroiXz8.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-08T03:14:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI see that the \u0022reactions / likes\u0022 button was messed up with for a brief period somewhen earlier of the month this post was created. Now it\u0027s back, but modified.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any chance to revert it back to it\u0027s old state, pre-messed\u00A0? It looks a bit odd, esp. from mobile, and is definitely less... reactive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-08T18:47:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223578167\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554693256\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298447\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022YNM\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, YNM said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any chance to revert it back\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E to it\u0027s old state, pre-\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Emessed\u00A0? It looks a bit odd, esp. from mobile, and is definitely less... reactive. \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t there are any plans to return the reaction button to its pre-April-Fools state. Apparently, it got messed up when the forums migrated from vBulletin, and the prank ended up fixing it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-08T20:02:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223578539\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554749260\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nApparently\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E, it got messed up when the forums migrated from vBulletin, and the prank ended up fixing it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think it\u0027s the exact case...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI remembered it when it was first implemented, including when other types of reactions was available. The resulting amount of like would be stored in a small box next to it. Right now, it\u0027s not like what it was... though if the devs feels happy with it, who am I to force such an insignificant change.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-09T00:02:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223578571\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554753763\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298447\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022YNM\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, YNM said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight now, it\u0027s not like what it was.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think we\u0027re closer to what we intended originally, might not be perfect, but it\u0027s better than it was last month.\u00A0 I don\u0027t see it changing soon unless something horrible is found.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"roboslacker","CreatedById":175473,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-09T12:03:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s the consensus on double posting on this forum?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-09T14:28:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223578981\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554811381\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175473\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022roboslacker\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, roboslacker said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s the consensus on double posting on this forum?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf the posts are made close enough in time to each other, they\u0027re automagically merged by the forum.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOther than that, there\u0027s no restrictions, so long as they follow all the forum rules.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-10T12:52:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223578715\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554768125\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/9/2019 at 7:02 AM, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think we\u0027re closer to what we intended originally, might not be perfect, but it\u0027s better than it was last month.\u00A0 I don\u0027t see it changing soon unless something horrible is found.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI see now. It works good from computer web browser, but it doesn\u0027t do very well on mobile browsers...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe splash and resulting blue often bugs out on mobile. I\u0027m usually on Google Chrome v73, in\u00A0Android 8.1.0 on SM-G610F.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-04-10T12:54:25Z\u0022 title=\u002204/10/2019 12:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EApril 10, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by YNM\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-10T23:36:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223578981\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554811381\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175473\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022roboslacker\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/9/2019 at 5:03 AM, roboslacker said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s the consensus on double posting on this forum?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat Dman said.\u00A0 Though bear in mind the rule against \u0022bumping\u0022-- for example, if you post a question, and it just sits there for a long time and you\u0027re getting impatient for an answer, it\u0027s not okay to post a second time just to try to bump the thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraston","CreatedById":188565,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-11T13:58:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223580173\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554939400\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit\u0027s\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E not okay to post a second time just to try to bump the thread.\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Dies a little inside*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-11T14:02:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223580585\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554991118\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188565\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fraston\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Fraston said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Dies a little inside*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs opposed to if we \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eallowed\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E it, in which case every time someone pollutes the forum with another \u0022bump\u0022, then \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eeveryone on the whole darn forum\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E dies a little inside?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0027Fraid we gotta pull a \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=19\u0026amp;v=Xa6c3OTr6yA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EVulcan-philosophy\u003C/a\u003E on this one, friend.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(It\u0027s one of those things that wouldn\u0027t be a problem, if just one person did it, and not too often.\u00A0 But if we allowed it, \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Emany\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E people would do it \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eall the time\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E, and the forum would just devolve into an endless content-free spew of \u0022bump\u0022 bilge, and the signal would get drowned out by all the noise.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraston","CreatedById":188565,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-11T14:07:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNevermind. It is more acceptable to \u201Cnecropost\u201D on forum games than it is anywhere else, as long as it is few and far between times, in my opinion. I revived \u201CKSP vending machine\u201D and I wasn\u2019t scolded...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-04-11T14:11:37Z\u0022 title=\u002204/11/2019 02:11  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EApril 11, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Fraston\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-11T14:45:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223580592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554991632\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188565\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fraston\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, Fraston said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNevermind. It is more acceptable to \u201Cnecropost\u201D on forum games than it is anywhere else, as long as it is few and far between times, in my opinion. I revived \u201CKSP vending machine\u201D and I wasn\u2019t scolded...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s no rule forbidding necroposting.\u00A0 Please be clear, \u003Cstrong\u003E\u0022bumping\u0022 is not the same thing as necroposting.\u00A0 Bumping is never okay.\u00A0 Necroposting often is.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat we mean by \u0022bumping\u0022 is if you post in a thread, \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eand then \u003Cstrong\u003Eyou\u003C/strong\u003E post in that same thread \u003Cstrong\u003Eagain\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E specifically for purposes of \u0022trying to keep your thread on top\u0022.\u00A0 Here\u0027s a classic example of what bumping looks like:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nThere\u0027s some mod thread somewhere, perhaps a low-traffic one that doesn\u0027t get posts very often.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nUser has problem.\u00A0 Posts a question.\u00A0 \u0022Help me, I\u0027ve got \u003Cem\u003E\u0026lt;problem\u0026gt;\u003C/em\u003E, can someone help?\u0022\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nA day goes by and nobody else posts anything.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThat same user gets impatient and then posts \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eagain\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E something like \u0022bump\u0022 or \u0022Anyone?\u0022 or the like.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s not allowed, because it serves no useful purpose and \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eis\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E highly annoying to other forum members-- it\u0027s like someone who rings a doorbell, and when they don\u0027t get an answer, just keeps ringing and ringing the doorbell trying to get someone to answer the door.\u00A0 Dude, you ring a doorbell \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eonce\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E.\u00A0 More than that is just annoying harassment.\u00A0 In the above example, #2 \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Emay\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E have been a \u0022necro\u0022 if the thread were long dormant... but it may be a reasonable one, and it\u0027s not \u0022bumping\u0022.\u00A0 #4, however, \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eis\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E bumping, and is not okay.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s in stark contrast to mere necroposting, which \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Esometimes\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E may be silly and pointless (e.g. reviving a thread which really needs to stay dead, such as a Gameplay Questions thread from a KSP version five years ago that\u0027s no longer relevant because KSP has changed since then).\u00A0 But there\u0027s also such a thing as a \u0022righteous necro\u0022, where the old thread may still be perfectly relevant, so there\u0027s nothing wrong with reviving it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor example, maybe there\u0027s a mod thread that hasn\u0027t had a post in a long time-- maybe it\u0027s just that not a lot\u0027s happening so nobody has had any reason to post recently.\u00A0 It\u0027s not \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Edead\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E, it\u0027s \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eresting\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u00A0 So asking a question there could be perfectly legitimate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr, take the example of the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/101246-ksps-vending-machine/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKSP\u0027s Vending Machine\u003C/a\u003E thread that you mention, in Forum Games:\u00A0 It sat around gathering dust for a couple of years, and then \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/101246-ksps-vending-machine/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=3577094\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eyou posted in it\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffff00;\u0022\u003EThat\u0027s not a bump.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0 So you didn\u0027t do anything even slightly \u0022wrong\u0022, and you\u0027re fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSure, I guess you could call that a \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Enecro\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E... but in this case, I think it\u0027s a perfectly fair one.\u00A0 That thread was gathering dust for a while, sure, but it\u0027s still just as \u0022valid\u0022 as it ever was, and nothing even slightly wrong with reviving it.\u00A0 As evidenced by the fact that people are having fun with it and continuing to post after you.\u00A0 So, ya done good.\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EExamples like this are \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ewhy\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E there\u0027s no actual rule against necroposting.\u00A0 It \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eoften\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E is somewhat inappropriate, but not always-- it depends on context.\u00A0 In this case, you\u0027re perfectly fine.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E(What \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ewould\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E have been \u0022bumping\u0022 would have been, suppose you posted in that game thread and then nobody posted after you for a while so you got impatient and posted \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eagain\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E to try to \u0022ring the doorbell\u0022.\u00A0 But you didn\u0027t do that, so you\u0027re good.)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lapis","CreatedById":193784,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-11T18:59:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64714-gargamel/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002264714\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64714-gargamel/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Gargamel\u003C/a\u003E how was the transition from normal forum user to mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-11T19:35:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223580875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221555009154\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022193784\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lapis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n36 minutes ago, lapis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64714-gargamel/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002264714\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64714-gargamel/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Gargamel\u003C/a\u003E how was the transition from normal forum user to mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe\u0027s recovering nicely and the implant scar is healing well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-11T23:34:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223580875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221555009154\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022193784\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lapis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, lapis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64714-gargamel/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002264714\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64714-gargamel/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Gargamel\u003C/a\u003E how was the transition from normal forum user to mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuite abrupt and jarring to be honest.\u00A0\u00A0 Once I sent the I accept Email, I figured it would take some time, hours to days before I was allowed in.\u00A0 Took like 3 minutes.\u00A0\u00A0 I refreshed to forums to look around, and all this new shiny stuff appeared.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 So I started pushing buttons.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 I apologize for that minor outage in January.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraston","CreatedById":188565,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-12T00:35:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you guys have a record of a user that acquired\u00A029\u00A0followers within their first year of \u00A0KSP foruming?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, besides me?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Csub\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003EHelp me\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:6px;\u0022\u003EI\u0027m drowning in followers and I\u00A0love it\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/sub\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-04-12T00:41:17Z\u0022 title=\u002204/12/2019 12:41  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EApril 12, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Fraston\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-12T00:38:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223580592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221554991632\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188565\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fraston\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Fraston said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNevermind. It is more acceptable to \u201Cnecropost\u201D on forum games than it is anywhere else, as long as it is few and far between times, in my opinion. I revived \u201CKSP vending machine\u201D and I wasn\u2019t scolded...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my opinion, it\u0027s quite alright to bring back an old forum game, and it actually kind of annoys me when someone makes a new, identical forum game just because the original hadn\u0027t been posted in in a long time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-12T00:57:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223581176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221555029481\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my opinion, it\u0027s quite alright to bring back an old forum game, and it actually kind of annoys me when someone makes a new, identical forum game just because the original hadn\u0027t been posted in in a long time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn that case, the best thing to do is report the new thread, and in the comments for the report, add a link to the old thread.\u00A0\u00A0 That way we can review if, in fact, they are similar threads, and we can merge them.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA thread being old doesn\u0027t mean it\u0027s dead.\u00A0 There are a lot of old threads that have lots of good info in them, and pertinent on topic \u0027bumps\u0027 are completely acceptable.\u00A0 That orange box warning a thread is old doesn\u0027t say \u0022Don\u0027t post here\u0022, it just says to consider whether it is appropriate to post there.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCase in point, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/187168-lisias/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022187168\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/187168-lisias/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Lisias\u003C/a\u003E did bump a 2 year old thread today, and it is exactly the type of necro/bump that we like to see.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5009929963\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/157781-the-kerbal-chronicles-winners/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:228px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JERONIMO","CreatedById":188491,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-12T01:45:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s you\u0027r average reply speed in time?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-12T02:13:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223581257\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221555033521\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188491\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JERONIMO\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n27 minutes ago, JERONIMO said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s you\u0027r average reply speed in time?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo what?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn this case.... 27 minutes apparently.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-12T03:27:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223581175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221555029338\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188565\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fraston\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Fraston said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you guys have a record of a user that acquired\u00A029\u00A0followers within their first year of \u00A0KSP foruming?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t tell if you\u0027re joking or not, but we don\u0027t keep records on that sort of thing.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}